{"data":[{"date":"07:26 30/06","title":"Southgate l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c \u201c\u0111\u00e0y\u201d Kane tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/southgate-ly-giai-viec-day-kane-tren-ghe-du-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 Kane tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Southgate d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1edbi 8 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho Anh th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 b\u1edfi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj. \u1ede v\u00f2ng 1/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Colombia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb World Cup 2006 t\u1edbi nay, Anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 \u1edf Iceland t\u1ea1i Euro 2016. Southgate, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Nga. \u00d4ng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Kane v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 Kane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 Kane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/HLV-Southgate.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 Kane d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t (\u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8), ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd\u201d, Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh. \u201cV\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t, trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Kane d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Kane \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n ph\u00fat n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 d\u00f9 \u0111ang kh\u00e1t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Kane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\u201d, Southgate l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Kane gi\u00e0nh Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng 1/8. Kane hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh v\u00e0 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee5c.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gary-cahill-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh-421-189768.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u201cdi\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-southgate-xac-nhan-kha-nang-giu-chan-harry-kane-o-tran-gap-dt-bi-421-189663.html\">HLV Southgate x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/wenger-chi-ra-mat-xich-yeu-kem-nhat-cua-dt-anh-421-189626.html\">Wenger ch\u1ec9 ra m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-martinez-to-ra-hai-long-sau-khi-lo-thang-anh-421-189914.html\">HLV Martinez t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng sau khi \u201cl\u1ee1\u201d th\u1eafng Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-that-bai-truoc-bi-466-189957.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tam-su-se-de-dang-tien-vao-tu-ket-421-189769.html\">Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"732","checkdouble":"189976"},{"date":"07:39 30/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 30/6: \"Tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng\" Mourinho b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-306-tro-cung-mourinho-bat-ngo-o-lai-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 30/6.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juve. </strong>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Giorgio Chiellini v\u00e0 Andrea Barzagli \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus. Trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Bianconeri \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Chiellini s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Juve th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m, trong khi Barzagli ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB n\u00e0y th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\"Tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng\" Mourinho \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U. </strong>Manchester United m\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng Marouane Fellaini \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t suy \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 khi c\u00f3 tin anh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Old Trafford d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 306 Tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Mourinho \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 306 Tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Mourinho \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-306-Tro-cung-Mourinho-o-lai-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Fellaini k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M.U d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Bonucci. </strong>Man United \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Leonardo Bonucci nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Man City hay Chelsea. T\u1edd Corriere dello Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh giao d\u1ecbch v\u1edbi AC Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Hierro s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3m De Gea \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T Nga?</strong> V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh David De Gea \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn Nga \u2013 T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV Fernando Hierro \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Colombia. </strong>Thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh l\u00e0 Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u00e2u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez cua Colombia\" title=\"James Rodriguez cua Colombia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/Arsenal-va-Chelsea-theo-duoi-James-Rodriguez-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 James Rodriguez</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng mua Willian, Barca v\u1eabn b\u1ecb Chelsea kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb.</strong> Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge m\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba\u201d t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, Barca m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m. </strong>Barca vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 n\u1ebfu\u2026</strong> Antoine Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 sau khi anh x\u00f3a \u0111i n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 Champions League v\u00e0 World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"731","checkdouble":"189977"},{"date":"07:57 30/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina (21h ng\u00e0y 30/6): Khi \u201cCh\u00faa c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf\u201d \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\u2026","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-argentina-21h-ngay-306-khi-chua-cuu-the-da-tro-lai.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Argentina nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cCh\u00faa c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf\u201d tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ee7a World Cup, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Argentina l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArgentina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n xu\u1ed1ng&hellip; \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 85, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn b\u1ecb Nigeria c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau khi h\u00f2a Iceland v\u00e0 thua Croatia. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00fang 1 ph\u00fat sau, m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 Marcos Rojo \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Gabriel Mercado, ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u00f9ng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho Argentina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ta n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Ch\u00faa \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i cho Argentina. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng s\u1eafm vai tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cuneyt Cakir \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 kh\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty. Ch\u00ednh Rojo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Argentina song t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng t\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR v\u1eabn n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n cho Nigeria.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina (21h ng\u00e0y 306) Khi Ch\u00faa tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina (21h ng\u00e0y 306) Khi Ch\u00faa tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Nhan-dinh-Phap-vs-Argentina-(21h-ngay-306)-Khi-Chua-tro-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Argentina \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNigeria b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfi, song Argentina th\u00ec nh\u01b0 h\u1ed3i sinh. D\u00f9 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean La Albiceleste \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y sinh kh\u00ed, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 h\u00ecnh dung sau khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMessi \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;n\u1ed5 s\u00fang&rdquo; tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona kho\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Lionel Messi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea1i \u0110T Argentina, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00f4i khi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf m\u00ecnh Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi ghi ban cho Argentina tai WC 2018\" title=\"Messi ghi ban cho Argentina tai WC 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Messi-ghi-ban-cho-Argentina-tai-WC-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cho Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nArgentina r\u1ed3i c\u00e1c HLV c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eb1m ph\u00e1t huy kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Messi. Nh\u01b0ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, C\u0110V x\u1ee9 Tango tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Leo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t khi c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, Argentina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u1ee9ng gi\u1eefa 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh La Albiceleste v\u00e0 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u hi\u1ebfm khi ch\u00fang ta th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-dt-phap-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-lionel-messi-421-189970.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/sao-dt-phap-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-lionel-messi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-dt-phap-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-lionel-messi-421-189970.html\">Sao \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110T Ph\u00e1p Hugo Lloris \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, n\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng minh vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a Messi t\u1ea1i Argentina v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o xanh tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ngay trong kh\u00e2u ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, HLV Jorge Sampaoli c\u0169ng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd Messi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. Ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria v\u00e0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Argentina mong s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u1edf ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 7 n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1p ch\u1edd h\u1ecd tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kazan Arena.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Phap vs Argentina\" title=\"Preview Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Phap-vs-Argentina.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina 21h ng\u00e0y 30/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nN\u1ed7i lo c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Australia 2-1 nh\u1edd 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb penalty v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. K\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng Peru 1-0 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Mbappe nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u1edbn, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lloris li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd d\u00f9 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n song ph\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ng\u1eafn qua l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 sau c\u00f9ng chia \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Argentina, Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Griezmann m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m penalty. Mbappe \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac h\u01a1i non n\u1edbt trong khi Giroud kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt ngo\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phap vs Peru Pavard phong ngu\" title=\"Phap vs Peru Pavard phong ngu\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Phap-vs-Peru-Pavard-phong-ngu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T&nbsp;Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a 3 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t. Nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, cho t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eddi s\u00e2n n\u1eeda sau hi\u1ec7p 2, Griezmann kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c n\u00e0o cho Giroud. Phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac d\u1eabm ch\u00e2n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Mbappe.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Pavard c\u00f2n b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Stuttgart h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t song th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn ph\u00eda sau l\u01b0ng. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai 22 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c \u1edf c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n l\u00e0 Lucas Hernandez c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1edfi c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng Peru.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn Samuel Umtiti nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c m\u00e0 Argentina t\u1ea1o ra ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u1edbn h\u01a1n 3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p tr\u1ea3i qua \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111ang t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u00f3 khi Les Bleus c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1 bay kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p (4-3-3): </strong>1.Lloris - 2.Pavard, 4.Varane, 5.Umtiti, 21.Hernandez - 6.Pogba, 13.Kante, 14.Matuidi - 10.Mbappe, 9.Giroud, 7.Griezmann.<br>\r\n<strong>Argentina (4-4-2): </strong>12.Armani - 2.Mercado, 17.Otamendi, 16.Rojo, 3.Tagliafico - 15.Perez, 14.Mascherano, 7.Banega, 11.Di Maria - 9.Higuain, 10.Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Argentina th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Phap vs Argentina\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Phap-vs-Argentina-(4-3-3-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/marcos-rojo-trai-nghiem-tu-than-va-khoanh-khac-cuu-ca-dan-toc-389-189739.html\">Marcos Rojo: Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eed th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc c\u1ee9u c\u1ea3 d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-21-vi-sao-messi-bi-xem-la-ke-phan-boi-421-189871.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 21: V\u00ec sao Messi b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 k\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/an-tuong-world-cup/messi-cung-albiceleste-cu-huych-nguoi-qua-nguong-cua-hep-471-189731.html\">B\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup: Messi c\u00f9ng Albiceleste - C\u00fa hu\u00fdch ng\u01b0\u1eddi qua ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-vuot-qua-vong-bang-tinh-than-albiceleste-hay-tro-lo-cua-fifa-421-189727.html\">Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng: Tinh th\u1ea7n Albiceleste hay tr\u00f2 l\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a FIFA?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/mascherano-argentina-xung-dang-voi-suat-du-vong-18-469-189726.html\">Mascherano: Argentina x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng 1/8</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"730","checkdouble":"189978"},{"date":"08:30 30/06","title":"\u0110T B\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn 3 tin m\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/dt-bi-nhan-3-tin-mung-truoc-tran-gap-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9, c\u1ef1u HLV Everton kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed9 ba Romelu Lukaku, Vincent Kompany v\u00e0 Thomas Vermaelen \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roberto Martinez b\u00e1o tin vui cho B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng G, B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/HLV-Roberto-Martinez-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Bi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lukaku \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRomelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 ghi hai b\u00e0n trong 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Panama v\u00e0 Tunisia nh\u01b0ng v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-anh-463-189888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs B\u1ec9 </span>v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 ch\u00e2n. Thomas Vermaelen ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00ec va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Vardy.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVincent Kompany d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi B\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9, c\u1ef1u HLV Everton kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed9 ba Romelu Lukaku, Vincent Kompany v\u00e0 Thomas Vermaelen \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;Romelu Lukaku \u0111ang h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c t\u1ed1t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t, Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Vermaelen kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Vincent Kompany \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong kho\u1ea3ng 20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roberto Martinez khen ng\u1ee3i Marouane Fellaini</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marouane Fellaini \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh, song kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Roberto Martinez v\u1eabn khen ng\u1ee3i c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fellaini o lai M.U\" title=\"Fellaini \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/cuc-bat-ngo-voi-ben-do-tiep-theo-cua-fellaini.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Fellaini</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao Fellaini l\u1ea1i hay b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao <br>\r\ngi\u1edd than phi\u1ec1n, v\u1edbi Fellaini \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn. B\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn khi Fellaini c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"729","checkdouble":"189979"},{"date":"08:44 30/06","title":"Casemiro: \"Neymar \u1edf c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/29/casemiro-neymar-o-cung-dang-cap-voi-ronaldo-va-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Casemiro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Neymar \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Casemiro \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Neymar</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u00f9ng vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Casemiro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Casemiro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Casemiro-phat-bieu-ve-Neymar-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Casemiro \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Neymar gi\u00fap Brazil v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Mexico \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. Casemiro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Neymar \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo v\u00e0 Messi l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. Theo t\u00f4i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi kh\u00e1c. Ngo\u00e0i 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Neymar, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi B\u0110N, Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf Argentina c\u00f2n Neymar l\u00e0 linh h\u1ed3n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Braizl. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/kaka-mach-nuoc-de-dt-brazil-bien-neymar-toa-sang-tai-world-cup-421-189811.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kaka c\u0169ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar</span>, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ef1u sao Brazil c\u00f2n b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Casemiro quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Mexico, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F. Chicharito v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c 1-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, song Casemiro v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Casemiro choi that vong truoc Thuy Sy\" title=\"Casemiro ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/paulinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Casemiro tin Brazil s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra kinh nghi\u1ec7m. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00fang th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ngo\u00e0i ra b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi 100% phong \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cMexico c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecd. Brazil \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"728","checkdouble":"189980"},{"date":"20:42 29/06","title":"Neymar, Messi v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/neymar-messi-vang-mat-trong-doi-hinh-tieu-bieu-vong-bang-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd Goal.com m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai si\u00eau sao Messi v\u00e0 Neymar.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i sau 48 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Ronaldo, Kane, Coutinho&hellip; song c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Messi, Neymar. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 khi Goal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf qua c\u1ea3 Messi l\u1eabn Neymar \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa hat-trick ngay tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n&nbsp;g\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi Ronaldo c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Goal.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi Neymar\" title=\"Messi Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/neymar-messi-vang-mat-trong-doi-hinh-tieu-bieu-vong-bang-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Messi, Neymar v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup c\u1ee7a Goal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh Ronaldo, Harry Kane c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. V\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho &lsquo;Tam S\u01b0&rsquo; Kane hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9, Kane v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i xa \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Goal \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ch\u1ec9 ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Morocco trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2, nh\u01b0ng vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Isco \u1edf &quot;Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa b\u00f2 t\u00f3t&quot; l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e0n anh gi\u00e0u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 Sergio Busquets, Koke, David Silva hay Andres Iniesta, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Costa. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng quan s\u00e1t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Isco.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Isco t\u1ea1i Real Madrid l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u00ea d\u1eaft v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Modric \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Croatia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Modric c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi pha s\u00fat xa \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Argentina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Goal nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi l\u00e0 N'Golo Kante. S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t v\u00e0 l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Kante gi\u00fap tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a &quot;G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois&quot; n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Hirving Lozano (c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i) v\u00e0 Philippe Coutinho (c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i). \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 hai ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Goal vinh danh l\u00e0 Domagoj Vida&nbsp;(Croatia), Yerry Mina&nbsp;(Colombia) v\u00e0 Diego Godin&nbsp;(Uruguay). \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Goal l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Robin Olsen (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u pha c\u1ee9u thua \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Mexico v\u1eeba qua. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 tung ra 18 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Mexico l\u00e0 20 l\u1ea7n tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1edd t\u00e0i ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Olsen m\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang 2 l\u1ea7n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Goal: (3-5-2)<br>\r\nRobin Olsen - Vida, Mina, Godin - Lozano, Kante, Isco, Modric, Coutinho - Ronaldo, Kane</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina-465-189933.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina-465-189933.html\">Samuel Umtiti: \u0110T Argentina kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Messi</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Barcelona nay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kaka-mach-nuoc-de-dt-brazil-bien-neymar-toa-sang-tai-world-cup-421-189811.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/kaka-mach-nuoc-de-dt-brazil-bien-neymar-toa-sang-tai-world-cup.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kaka-mach-nuoc-de-dt-brazil-bien-neymar-toa-sang-tai-world-cup-421-189811.html\">Kaka m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Brazil gi\u00fap Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Kaka tin r\u1eb1ng BHL \u0110T Brazil n\u00ean h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi c\u00e1ch ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/coutinho-quan-trong-khong-kem-neymar-tren-tuyen-brazil-421-189481.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/coutinho-quan-trong-khong-kem-neymar-tren-tuyen-brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/coutinho-quan-trong-khong-kem-neymar-tren-tuyen-brazil-421-189481.html\">Coutinho quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m Neymar tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Brazil</span><br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Roberto Carlos ca ng\u1ee3i ng\u00f4i sao Barcelona sau hai m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 Costa Rica.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"727","checkdouble":"189960"},{"date":"22:08 29/06","title":"Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Colombia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/arsenal-va-chelsea-theo-duoi-ngoi-sao-dt-colombia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng khi \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n xu\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Joachim Loew cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>HLV Joachim Loew v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Joachim Loew v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Joachim Loew v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/hlv-joachim-loew-van-chua-het-soc-sau-khi-tro-ve-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Joachim Loew v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mang t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m nh\u01b0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u00ea ch\u1ec1 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u00e3 4 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ch\u00ednh HLV Joachim Loew m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o nhanh sau khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1p xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n bay t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Frankfurt \u0111\u00eam 28/6,\u00a0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \"Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u01a1n l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 xin l\u1ed7i C\u0110V. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 qu\u00ean \u0111i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfp theo\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Theo m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Bild (\u0110\u1ee9c) th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 80% C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c (DFB) sa th\u1ea3i HLV Loew. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch DFB, \u00f4ng Reinhard Grindel cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00e1n sa th\u1ea3i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c d\u00e0nh cho chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 58 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 DFB c\u0169ng v\u1eeba gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho HLV Joachim Loew, gi\u00fap \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Die Mannschaft t\u1edbi h\u1ebft VCK World Cup 2022.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-duc-thieu-gi-va-thua-gi-de-phai-ngam-ngui-roi-world-cup-421-189876.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/goc-nhin-duc-thieu-gi-va-thua-gi-de-phai-ngam-ngui-roi-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-duc-thieu-gi-va-thua-gi-de-phai-ngam-ngui-roi-world-cup-421-189876.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110\u1ee9c thi\u1ebfu g\u00ec v\u00e0 th\u1eeba g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i r\u1eddi World Cup?</span><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 hai th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-duc-ve-nuoc-som-boi-khong-co-hoa-hong-cho-nguoi-duc-tren-dat-nga-168-189858.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/dt-duc-ve-nuoc-som-boi-khong-co-hoa-hong-cho-nguoi-duc-tren-dat-nga.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-duc-ve-nuoc-som-boi-khong-co-hoa-hong-cho-nguoi-duc-tren-dat-nga-168-189858.html\">\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm: B\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hoa h\u1ed3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga</span><br>\r\n\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qua n\u1ed5i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ea5t Nga l\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-dt-duc-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-2018-cung-su-chuan-bi-toi-te-421-189937.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/goc-nhin-dt-duc-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-2018-cung-su-chuan-bi-toi-te.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-dt-duc-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-2018-cung-su-chuan-bi-toi-te-421-189937.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e2u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7</span><br>\r\n\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi \u0111a ph\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu theo s\u00e1t h\u1ecd trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n n\u1eeda n\u0103m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"726","checkdouble":"189966"},{"date":"22:30 29/06","title":"HLV Hierro s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3m De Gea \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T Nga?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hlv-hierro-se-tram-de-gea-o-tran-dau-voi-dt-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh David De Gea \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn Nga \u2013 T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 HLV Hierro \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>HLV Hierro v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a David De Gea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hierro s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3m De Gea \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Hierro s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3m De Gea \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/khi-nhung-buoc-chan-run-ray.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Hierro v\u1eabn tin v\u00e0o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a De Gea</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i CLB Man United, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 pha l\u00f3ng ng\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi sau c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi Iran nh\u01b0ng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eb7p Morocco, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n MU c\u0169ng b\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng nh\u00e0 ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch b\u1eaft l\u00f3ng ng\u00f3ng, thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin. Anh khi\u1ebfn \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n song may m\u1eafn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp s\u1eeda sai \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap La Roja \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, De Gea \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi lo ng\u1ea1i. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i \u0111ang g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p y\u00eau c\u1ea7u HLV Hierro trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f2n \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Ateltico Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd AS c\u00f2n l\u00e0m h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c th\u0103m d\u00f2 v\u00e0 50% trong s\u1ed1 g\u1ea7n 40 ng\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 mu\u1ed1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ed5i De Gea v\u00e0 thay b\u1eb1ng Arrizabalaga. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u01a1n v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 HLV Hierro v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng De Gea. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i:<em> \"De Gea s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n. T\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga\".</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Hierro c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 tuy nhi\u00ean \u00f4ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 c\u00f9ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, vi\u1ec7c T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Nga \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-22-marocco-dau-roi-bong-dang-nha-vua-421-189595.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/tay-ban-nha-22-marocco-dau-roi-bong-dang-nha-vua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-22-marocco-dau-roi-bong-dang-nha-vua-421-189595.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Morocco: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng nh\u00e0 vua</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam kh\u00f3 qu\u00ean t\u1ea1i Kaliningrad, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t Morocco \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t La Roja h\u00f9ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, CLB Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus c\u1ee7a Man City trong  k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-421-189565.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-421-189565.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau m\u00e0n \u201ch\u00fat ch\u1ebft\u201d c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim kinh d\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kaliningrad. \u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecdng l\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"725","checkdouble":"189968"},{"date":"23:44 29/06","title":"Sao \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/sao-dt-phap-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-lionel-messi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110T Ph\u00e1p Hugo Lloris \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi.</h2><h2>Hugo Lloris c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Messi</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Argentina \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh khi m\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hugo Lloris c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hugo Lloris c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Hugo-Lloris-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-Lionel-Messi-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Hugo Lloris c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Messi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lloris \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Argentina, Lionel Messi. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 31 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng Lionel Messi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lloris \u00a0cho bi\u1ebft: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110T Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u1ec1 Argentina nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Messi v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n m\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa Messi v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p Kylian Mbappe, Lloris n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cMessi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai kh\u00e1c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKylian l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y nhanh nh\u1eb9n, thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng h\u01a1n c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Kylian c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina-465-189933.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina-465-189933.html\">Samuel Umtiti: \u0110T Argentina kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Messi</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Barcelona nay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-phap-canh-bao-dung-hy-vong-mot-messi-cua-barcelona-o-argentina-421-189897.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nguoi-phap-canh-bao-dung-hy-vong-mot-messi-cua-barcelona-o-argentina.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-phap-canh-bao-dung-hy-vong-mot-messi-cua-barcelona-o-argentina-421-189897.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o: \u201c\u0110\u1eebng hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t Messi c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u1edf Argentina\u201d</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i si\u00eau sao \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"724","checkdouble":"189970"},{"date":"00:03 30/06","title":"HLV Joachim Loew v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hlv-joachim-loew-van-chua-het-soc-sau-khi-tro-ve-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng khi \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n xu\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Joachim Loew cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>HLV Joachim Loew v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Joachim Loew v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Joachim Loew v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/hlv-joachim-loew-van-chua-het-soc-sau-khi-tro-ve-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Joachim Loew v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mang t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m nh\u01b0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u00ea ch\u1ec1 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u00e3 4 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ch\u00ednh HLV Joachim Loew m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft s\u1ed1c khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o nhanh sau khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1p xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n bay t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Frankfurt \u0111\u00eam 28/6,\u00a0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \"Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u01a1n l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 xin l\u1ed7i C\u0110V. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 qu\u00ean \u0111i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfp theo\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Theo m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Bild (\u0110\u1ee9c) th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 80% C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c (DFB) sa th\u1ea3i HLV Loew. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch DFB, \u00f4ng Reinhard Grindel cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00e1n sa th\u1ea3i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c d\u00e0nh cho chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 58 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 DFB c\u0169ng v\u1eeba gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho HLV Joachim Loew, gi\u00fap \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Die Mannschaft t\u1edbi h\u1ebft VCK World Cup 2022.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-duc-thieu-gi-va-thua-gi-de-phai-ngam-ngui-roi-world-cup-421-189876.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/goc-nhin-duc-thieu-gi-va-thua-gi-de-phai-ngam-ngui-roi-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-duc-thieu-gi-va-thua-gi-de-phai-ngam-ngui-roi-world-cup-421-189876.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110\u1ee9c thi\u1ebfu g\u00ec v\u00e0 th\u1eeba g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i r\u1eddi World Cup?</span><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 hai th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-duc-ve-nuoc-som-boi-khong-co-hoa-hong-cho-nguoi-duc-tren-dat-nga-168-189858.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/dt-duc-ve-nuoc-som-boi-khong-co-hoa-hong-cho-nguoi-duc-tren-dat-nga.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-duc-ve-nuoc-som-boi-khong-co-hoa-hong-cho-nguoi-duc-tren-dat-nga-168-189858.html\">\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm: B\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hoa h\u1ed3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga</span><br>\r\n\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qua n\u1ed5i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ea5t Nga l\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-dt-duc-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-2018-cung-su-chuan-bi-toi-te-421-189937.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/goc-nhin-dt-duc-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-2018-cung-su-chuan-bi-toi-te.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-dt-duc-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-2018-cung-su-chuan-bi-toi-te-421-189937.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e2u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7</span><br>\r\n\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi \u0111a ph\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu theo s\u00e1t h\u1ecd trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n n\u1eeda n\u0103m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"723","checkdouble":"189971"},{"date":"06:05 30/06","title":"Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 n\u1ebfu\u2026","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/griezmann-se-chuyen-toi-giai-nha-nghe-my-neu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Antoine Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 sau khi anh x\u00f3a \u0111i n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 Champions League v\u00e0 World Cup.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>N\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League c\u00f9ng Atletico Madrid \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Marseille, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, Griezmann \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Atletico, ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Barcelona hay m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u hi\u1ebfm hoi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Griezmann c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i CLB l\u1eabn \u0110TQG. Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2015/16, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f9ng Atletico th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Sau \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Euro 2016, anh l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Griezmann-se-chuyen-toi-giai-Nha-nghe-My-MLS-trong-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Griezmann m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 MLS</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGriezmann \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng Atletico v\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac chu\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1998. Sau \u0111\u00f3, theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m sang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7, ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng?\u201d, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Le Figaro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00f3 ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i MLS v\u00e0o khi n\u00e0o, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Khi t\u00f4i g\u1ea7n 32 hay 33 tu\u1ed5i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Griezmann \u0111ang c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 g\u1eb7p Argentina v\u00e0o 21h t\u1ed1i nay (30/6).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-dt-phap-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-lionel-messi-421-189970.html\">Sao \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina-465-189933.html\">Samuel Umtiti: \u0110T Argentina kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-phap-canh-bao-dung-hy-vong-mot-messi-cua-barcelona-o-argentina-421-189897.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o: \u201c\u0110\u1eebng hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t Messi c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u1edf Argentina\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-phap-vs-dan-mach-hoa-nhat-man-ru-ngu-o-luzhniki-421-189692.html\">Ph\u00e1p b\u1eaft tay \u0110an M\u1ea1ch h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t: \u0110i\u1ec7u ru ng\u1ee7 \u1edf Luzhniki</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-len-tieng-sau-tran-hoa-00-truoc-dan-mach-421-189682.html\">HLV \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"722","checkdouble":"189972"},{"date":"06:29 30/06","title":"\u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba\u201d t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, Barca m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/nguoi-thua-toa-sang-tai-world-cup-barca-mung-tham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mina t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, \u0110T Colombia b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o. \u0110\u00fang nh\u1eefng l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh d\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan v\u00e0 Senegal. \u1ede c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3, Yerry Mina \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Mina m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan, gi\u00fap Colombia tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 chung cu\u1ed9c. K\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh trung v\u1ec7 23 cao 1m95 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/yerry-mina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u l\u00e0m C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Senegal. Trong th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Colombia, c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Barcelona l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nBarca m\u1eebng v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia t\u1ea1i CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Barcelona. Barca vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina song l\u00e0 b\u1edfi l\u00fd do ngo\u00e0i chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. Trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Ernesto Valverde tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Yerry Mina\" title=\"trung ve Yerry Mina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/yerry-mina-khong-noi-nen-loi-sau-man-ra-mat-la-liga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Thomas Vermaelen. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Mina v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca. Ho\u1eb7c h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t anh, ho\u1eb7c s\u1ebd cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u00e2n Barca nh\u01b0 Sport hay Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c Mina. Song h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Blaugrana tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn h\u01a1n khi b\u00e1n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nFenerbahce l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1edbi Mina. Nh\u01b0ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng b\u1edfi hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng th\u0103ng hoa, \u0111\u1ed9 \u201chot\u201d c\u1ee7a anh l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng d\u00e2ng cao.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia-180-189646.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-va-real-dai-chien-vi-sao-bayern-munich-180-189512.html\">Barca v\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-va-real-muon-mua-thiago-alcantara-180-189489.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca vs Real v\u00ec sao tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"721","checkdouble":"189973"},{"date":"06:46 30/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (30/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-3062018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width: