iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luis Suarez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barcelona nh\u1eafn Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 \u0111i l\u00ean</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuis Suarez \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i khi Uruguay v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ai C\u1eadp 1-0 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i khi ghi b\u00e0n trong c\u1ea3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia 1-0 v\u00e0 Nga 3-0. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nQua \u0111\u00f3, Suarez c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\u201d, Suarez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. \u201c\u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7u to\u00e0n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luis Suarez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luis Suarez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Luis-Suarez-tai-Uruguay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Suarez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra, n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Uruguay chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi Uruguay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Barcelona l\u00e0 Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Jordi Alba. \u201cM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d, Suarez n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. D\u01b0 lu\u1eadn lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Edinson Cavani, Suarez cho hay: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft nhau t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nhau h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m cho \u0110TQG. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f9ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho Uruguay v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nhau c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Uruguay tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo-421-189843.html\">Uruguay kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-vui-dap-nga-man-trinh-dien-an-tuong-cua-nhung-hang-hot-421-189571.html\">Uruguay v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Nga: M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u201ch\u00e0ng hot\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/suarez-no-tung-bung-sau-khi-da-bai-nga-469-189566.html\">Suarez n\u1ed5 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng sau khi \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-nga-da-biet-truoc-chung-toi-van-bat-luc-truoc-uruguay-421-189563.html\">HLV Nga: \u201c\u0110\u00e3 bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-tabarez-phat-bieu-sau-tran-uruguay-30-nga-421-189561.html\">HLV Uruguay n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n v\u00f9i d\u1eadp ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"719","checkdouble":"189975"},{"date":"14:56 29/06","title":"Chi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Real v\u1ee5 sao Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/chi-62-trieu-bang-chelsea-vuot-mat-real-vu-sao-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, Marca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Chelsea r\u1ea5t \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi The Blues. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois co mot tran dau xuat sac\" title=\"Courtois c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Liverpool-mua-Thibaut-Courtois-khong-the-xay-ra-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Courtois ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Courtois kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;L\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin s\u1edf d\u0129 Courtois v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u1eabn nu\u00f4i \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i TBN \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n t\u1ee5 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/ramos-va-ronaldo-muon-real-mua-thu-mon-cua-chelsea-180-181590.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 thay Navas. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m, Real c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n chi kho\u1ea3ng 30 \u0111\u1ebfn 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm Alisson mua Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Courtois gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Chelsea c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay th\u1ebf. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Liverpool-muon-mua-Nick-Pope-cua-Burnley-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea chi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, Marca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monchi c\u1ee7a Roma kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Olympico \u1edf H\u00e8 2018: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Roma, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Roma v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia. Theo \u0111\u00f3, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois \u0111\u1ebfn Real, The Blues s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"718","checkdouble":"189942"}]}